      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "welcome back\n",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "Having friends..... I feel like its like a value thing you know",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "Like if you're in the same context as someone, and they are willing to socialize, then it is quite easy. ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "what do you mean? can you elaborate?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "Like \"I value something, I talk and know you value something, so I feel open to share that thing I value, and possibly my life\" ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "If I know you don't care about my life if I share it once, then it becomes much more difficult to share that cause I know you don't care.",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "its about sharing the right stuff with the right people I guess",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "hmm\n",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "interesting ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "what if I know everyone and constantly share things they find interesting, but they don't share things they find interesting to me?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "hmm\n",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "maybe ask them for it?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "people aren't as socialiable these days",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "say",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "I admire your bravery asking this to a stranger.",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "complaining to a stranger about being a lonely person is quite a loser behavior in modern societal norms",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "Ey man why are you talking\n",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "You seem to know lot about being lonely yourself",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
