    },
    {
      "content": "oh btw this is interesteing ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "I saw an article today about \"universe 25\" ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "a guy gave all the rats in a colony inifinite resources ",
