      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "but the colony evolved with stronger rats showing significant strengths. With weaker worker rats no longer needing to work, they all lost meaning, so all the female rats went for the strong rat and homosextuallity became rampant",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "Kurisu"
    },
    {
      "content": "and the society collapsed ",
